    tmp = 0.0
    v0 = (tmp * ((tmp + 0.13 + v2 + 0.88) / (tmp + 0.20 + v2 + 0.28)))
    tmp = 0.91
    tmp = ((wp.exp(v0 + 0.35) / 0.80) - wp.exp(wp.sin(v1 + 0.70)))
    v0 = (wp.exp((v0 + 0.62 * v0 + 0.20)) - (0.50 - wp.cos(v1 + 0.25)))
    v0 = wp.sin(tmp)
    tmp = (wp.abs((tmp + 0.38 / tmp + 0.37)) + (0.14 * v1))
    v1 = ((wp.abs(v2 + 0.47) / tmp) * (v2 + 0.95))
    data[tid] = v0
